=2006 |publisher=Amsterdam University Press |isbn=978-90-5629-428-1 |pages=261\u2013290 |access-date=25 November 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160501212840/https://books.google.com/books?id=u8gZklxHTMUC&pg=PA261 |archive-date=1 May 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref name=\"Bennie2017\">{{cite book|author=Lynn Bennie|editor1=Oscar Mazzoleni|editor2=Sean Mueller|chapter=The Scottish National Party: Nationalism for the many|title=Regionalist Parties in Western Europe: Dimensions of Success|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=aiolDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA22|year=2017|publisher=Taylor & Francis|isbn=978-1-317-06895-2|pages=22\u201341}}</ref><br />[[Social democracy]]<ref name=\"auto\">{{cite web |url=http://www.snp.org/about-us |title=About Us |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150913014940/http://www.snp.org/about-us |archivedate=13 September 2015 |df=dmy-all }}</ref><ref name=\"Hepburn20139\">{{cite book |author=Eve Hepburn |title=New Challenges for Stateless Nationalist and Regionalist Parties |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dTOOAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA9 |date=18 October 2013 |publisher=Routledge |isbn=978-1-317-96596-1 |page=9 |access-date=25 November 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160502074029/https://books.google.com/books?id=dTOOAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA9 |archive-date=2 May 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref name=\"Lingard\">{{cite book |author=Bob Lingard |title=Politics, Policies and Pedagogies in Education: The Selected Works of Bob Lingard |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2dopAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA120 |date=24 July 2013 |publisher=Routledge |isbn=978-1-135-01998-3 |page=120 |access-date=25 November 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510125745/https://books.google.com/books?id=2dopAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA120 |archive-date=10 May 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref><br />[[Pro-Europeanism]]\u200c<ref name=\"auto2\">{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2019/may/14/anti-brexit-feeling-help-snp-european-elections |